---
// Reserva con 2 calendarios lado a lado
---

<section class="section" id="reservar">
  <h2 class="section-title">Reserva tu cita</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Elige la modalidad que prefieras. Consulta presencial en Centro MÃ©dico Arboleda (Boadilla del Monte) o consulta online.</p>

  <div class="reserva-grid">
    <div class="reserva-card">
      <div class="reserva-card-header">
        <h3>Consulta presencial</h3>
        <p>Boadilla del Monte</p>
      </div>
      <iframe src="https://calendly.com/nutricionista-mariadelavera/primera-consulta?hide_event_type_details=1&hide_gdpr_banner=1" loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="reserva-card">
      <div class="reserva-card-header">
        <h3>Consulta online</h3>
        <p>Google Meet</p>
      </div>
      <iframe src="https://calendly.com/nutricionista-mariadelavera/primera-consulta-online?hide_event_type_details=1&hide_gdpr_banner=1" loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reserva-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .reserva-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    position: relative;
  }

  .reserva-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 90px;
    height: 90px;
    background: var(--white);
    z-index: 2;
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius) 0 0;
  }

  .reserva-card-header {
    padding: 20px 24px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .reserva-card-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.05em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .reserva-card-header p {
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .reserva-card iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 660px;
    border: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .reserva-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .reserva-card-header h3 { font-size: 0.95em; }
    .reserva-card-header p { font-size: 0.78em; }
    .reserva-card iframe { height: 600px; }
  }
</style>
